<h2 id="example-of-demonstrative-pronoun-from-papygreek-corpus">Example
of demonstrative pronoun from PapyGreek corpus</h2>
<ol type="1">
<li><strong>αὕτη</strong> γὰρ μού ἐστιν εὐχή.<br>
(<strong>haútē</strong> gàr moú estin eukhḗ.)<br>
<em>This is my prayer.</em><br>
<a href="https://papygreek.com/text/23097">p.bour.25.</a>, 6 (sent. 3),
transl. Bagnall - Cribiore (2006) p.&nbsp;260.</li>
</ol>
