<h2 id="discussion">Discussion</h2>
<ul>
<li>ὅδε is formed from the old demonstrative ὁ, ἡ, τό (Smyth 333), and
we have the article/old demonstrative used in papyri (See <a href="https://papygreek.com/grammar/101">4.4</a> on the definite article
and <span class="citation" data-cites="bhat2013">Bhat (2013)</span></li>
<li>deictic iota used in papyri with demonstratives?</li>
</ul>
